 biomes. Spiders require a 3x2x3 open space to spawn.\\n- Stray: "},{"text":"See How to get Husks, Strays, and Slimes","color":"dark_blue","clickEvent":{"action":"run_command","value":"/function give_a_book:husks_strays_slimes"}},{"text":".\\n- Vex: ","color":"reset"},{"text":"Evokers","color":"dark_blue","clickEvent":{"action":"change_page","value":"10"}},{"text":" can spawn them.","color":"reset"}]','["",{"text":"- Vindicator: Spawns during raids. ("},{"text":"See Inviting Pillager Patrols","color":"dark_blue","clickEvent":{"action":"run_command","value":"/function give_a_book:invite_patrols"}},{"text":" and ","color":"reset"},{"text":"See Establishing a Village","color":"dark_blue","clickEvent":{"action":"run_command","value":"/function give_a_book:make_village"}},{"text":")","color":"reset"}]','{"text":"- Witch: Uncommonly spawns in most overworld biomes. Contrary to common belief, their spawn rate is not increased in Swamp Biomes (unless you are near a swamp hut which does not spawn in this world). Or if a Villager is struck by lightning it will become a Witch."}','["",{"text":"- Wither Skeleton: Spawns in Nether Fortresses.\\n- Zoglin: "},{"text":"See Getting Striders, Hoglins, and Zoglins","color":"dark_blue","clickEvent":{"action":"run_command","value":"/function give_a_book:striders_hoglins_zoglins"}},{"text":".\\n- Zombie: In most overworld biomes.","color":"reset"}]','{"text":"- Zombie Villager: Uncommonly in most overworld biomes. Or If a Villager gets killed by a Zombie, it becomes a Zombie Villager (0% on Easy, 50% on Normal, 100% on Hard)."}','{"text":"- Zombified Piglin: Spawn in Nether Wastes and Crimson Forest Biomes on most solid blocks other than nether wart blocks at a low light level. They can randomly show up in an overworld Nether Portal."}'],title:"Technical Skyblock Guidebook",author:"Procymbopteryx and Kitty_McTophat",display:{Lore:['{"text":"Hostile Mob Spawning Mechanics"}']}}
